title: 71 Spring St
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 299542808', 'Rent: $2,695 / Month', 'Beds: 3', 'Bath: 2', 'Available Date: 08/01/2022', 'Pet: No Pets', 'Great credit and income required.', 'IF STUDENTS: a parent co-signer is required to guarantee the lease.', 'Maximum occupancy: 4 people.', 'Available 8/1!', 'Great opportunity to be in Bridgewater Center and minutes from BSU campus!', 'Great lovely, clean, and modern unit!', '3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this is a great size unit with high ceilings and hardwoods throughout.', 'Carpet in the bedrooms.', 'Laundry IN-UNIT.', 'Large eat-in kitchen and TWO bathrooms!', 'Almost 1000 sq ft of living space!', "Don't miss out on this one!", 'The landlords are asking for First, Last, and Security, and we charge a 1/2 month Broker Fee.', 'Total of $7000.00 to move in.', 'NO PETS ALLOWED at this rental.', 'Gas, Electric, and Water utilities are the tenants responsibility - building utilities are separately metered.', 'Snow plowing, landscaping are included in the rent.', '2 Parking spots at an additional cost 25.00 per spot per month to be paid in advance.', 'Please EMAIL ONLY for showings!', 'Northeast Realty & Co Quincy Office', 'FEATURES', 'Hardwood Floors', 'High Ceilings', 'Laundry in Unit', 'Refrigerator']
